# Zurvan Linux - M1.1a minimal proof-build package list
#
# Intentionally tiny. Validates that live-build produces a bootable ISO
# inside the GitHub Actions privileged container. No desktop environment,
# no custom configuration - those land in M1.1b.

## Live-system boot helpers (overlay/squashfs root at boot)
live-boot
live-config

## Kernel (metapackage pulls the current amd64 kernel)
linux-image-amd64

## Minimal CLI comfort set
sudo
locales
ca-certificates
iproute2
iputils-ping
